// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/43GGR3 hexagon three square prisms pack, 2024 jt

// Trying to understand the structure from Matt Parker's
// https://www.youtube.com/@standupmaths
// "New 7-direction pencil model discovered".
// https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MesBw3gF6Vs
// So far three square prisms & one hexagonal prism packed.

// Full structure here: https://www.shadertoy.com/view/l3GGR3 seven direction pencil structure

// tags: hexagon, square, prism, packing, lattice, rods, unit

